items.name: Spicy Sizzle Tacos
items.description: Tantalize your taste buds with these sizzling tacos featuring marinated and grilled meats, topped with a spicy kick. You'll be begging for more!

items.name: Carnivore's Delight Tacos
items.description: For the true meat lovers out there, our Carnivore's Delight Tacos boast a mouthwatering selection of beef, chicken, and pork, perfectly seasoned to perfection.

items.name: Zesty Veggie Fiesta Tacos
items.description: Vegetarian bliss in every bite! Our Zesty Veggie Fiesta Tacos showcase a colorful medley of fresh veggies, drizzled with a zesty sauce. A fiesta for your taste buds!

items.name: Fisherman's Catch Tacos
items.description: Dive into the ocean's flavors with our Fisherman's Catch Tacos. Featuring succulent fish, fresh salsa, and a hint of lime, it's a seafood sensation in every bite.

items.name: Smoky Chipotle Chicken Tacos
items.description: Savor the smoky goodness of our Chipotle Chicken Tacos. Tender chicken, grilled to perfection, and topped with a smoky chipotle sauce that will leave you craving more.

items.name: Burrito Bonanza
items.description: Experience a flavor explosion in every bite! Our Burrito Bonanza is a delightful combination of savory fillings wrapped in a warm tortilla. It's a fiesta in your mouth!

items.name: Tropical Heatwave Burrito
items.description: Spice up your life with the Tropical Heatwave Burrito. Packed with tropical flavors and a hint of heat, it's a fiesta for your taste buds!

items.name: Carnitas Carnival Burrito
items.description: Step right up to the Carnitas Carnival! This burrito features slow-cooked carnitas, savory black beans, and a carnival of flavors that'll make your taste buds dance.

items.name: Veggie Fiesta Burrito
items.description: Join the Veggie Fiesta with our mouthwatering burrito packed full of fresh vegetables, seasoned rice, and a burst of flavorful sauces. Vegetarian delight at its finest!

items.name: Chili Con Carne Burrito
items.description: Warm up your taste buds with our Chili Con Carne Burrito. Filled with hearty chili, seasoned beef, and all the fixings, it's a comforting hug in a tortilla.

items.name: Dulce de Leche Delight
items.description: Indulge your sweet tooth with our Dulce de Leche Delight dessert. A delectable treat that will transport you to a world of sweetness and satisfaction.

items.name: ChocoChurro Extravaganza
items.description: Dive into the delightful combination of crispy churros coated in rich chocolate. It's not just a dessert; it's a ChocoChurro Extravaganza!

items.name: Tres Leches Temptation
items.description: Satisfy your cravings with our Tres Leches Temptation. A moist and decadent cake soaked in three types of milk, creating a heavenly dessert experience.

items.name: Mango Tango Sorbet
items.description: Dance into a world of tropical bliss with our Mango Tango Sorbet. A refreshing and fruity treat that will leave your taste buds doing the tango!

items.name: Cinnamon Churro Explosion
items.description: Experience an explosion of flavor with our Cinnamon Churro Explosion. Crispy churros rolled in cinnamon sugar, served with a side of pure joy.
